Thank you, Liza.

213
00:10:57,030 --> 00:10:57,780
马上就好了
Won't be long.

214
00:10:57,780 --> 00:10:58,860
我等会儿再来
I'll come back.

215
00:11:03,140 --> 00:11:04,720
