I asked you a question.

216
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:09,680
显然  您这儿有个内奸
Oh, you have a mole, obviously.

217
00:11:11,210 --> 00:11:13,420
玩这套可不是马罗尼的强项  不是吗
Which is not Maroni's forte, is it?

218
00:11:13,530 --> 00:11:15,140
这是别人干的
No, this is someone else.

219
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:16,610
某个狡猾的人
Someone artful.

220
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:18,510
