She has proved her disloyalty a hundred times.

227
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:35,550
她想要杀您
She wants your head.

228
00:11:36,350 --> 00:11:38,620
半数为我工作的人都有这想法
Like half the people who work for me.

229
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:41,170
菲什为我赚了很多钱
Fish makes me a lot of money.

230
00:11:41,340 --> 00:11:42,460
我可以对付菲什・穆尼
I can handle Fish Mooney,

231
00:11:42,460 --> 00:11:44,810
