or whatever son of a bitch did this to me.

232
00:11:45,520 --> 00:11:47,400
告诉我怎么找出奸细
Tell me how to find the mole.

233
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:50,090
您就交给我吧  法尔科内阁下
You leave that to me, Don Falcone.

234
00:11:51,390 --> 00:11:52,540
这是脏活儿
Dirty work.

235
00:11:52,730 --> 00:11:54,470
我会为您找出奸细的
I'll find your mole for you.

236
00:11:54,930 --> 00:11:55,940
