Bring me proof.

239
00:12:08,990 --> 00:12:10,090
我不明白
I don't get it.

240
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,820
你  盖布  不明白
You, Gabe? Not get it?

241
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:14,450
令人惊奇啊
Quelle surprise.

242
00:12:15,340 --> 00:12:16,960
说说吧  你哪里不明白
What, pray, don't you get?

243
00:12:17,610 --> 00:12:19,900
为什么不告诉法尔科内真相
Why not just tell Falcone the truth?

244
00:12:21,230 --> 00:12:23,500
是那个莉莎背叛了他
It was that Liza girl that betrayed him.

245
00:12:24,150 --> 00:12:25,480
时机  盖布利尔
Timing, Gabriel.

246
00:12:26,350 --> 00:12:27,690
时机就是一切
Timing is everything.

247
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:30,840
莉莎就是一枚定时炸弹
And Liza is a time bomb.

248
00:12:31,330 --> 00:12:32,150
你就...
Just...

249
00:12:33,210 --> 00:12:34,280
等上一阵子
wait a while.

250
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,140
然后好好看着学着吧
Then watch and learn.

251
00:12:39,020 --> 00:12:40,620
待在那里以防他出现
Stay there in case he shows.

252
00:12:42,110 --> 00:12:43,020
洛夫克拉夫特不在家
Lovecraft isn't at home.

253
00:12:43,020 --> 00:12:44,560
管家从昨天就没见到他了
Housekeeper hasn't seen him since yesterday.

254
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:45,920
艾伦说他没去办公室
Allen says he didn't come into his office.

255
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:47,200
