professional assassins coming after them.

262
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,630
布鲁斯和塞琳娜可能会死
Bruce and Selina could end up dead.

263
00:12:59,630 --> 00:13:01,400
我们会让洛夫克拉夫特叫停他们的
We're gonna get Lovecraft to call them off.

264
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:03,840
他们怎么知道的
How did they know?

265
00:13:04,990 --> 00:13:06,190
我从没告诉过你她的名字
I never told you her name,

266
00:13:06,190 --> 00:13:07,560
更别说她藏在哪里了
let alone where she was hiding,

267
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:09,760
-所以你不可能...  -我当然不会
- so you couldn't have... - I should say not.

268
00:13:11,270 --> 00:13:13,810
你也没向任何人提过我的名字  对吗
And you never mentioned my name to anyone, right?

269
00:13:13,910 --> 00:13:14,680
没有  我们说好的
No, we agreed.

270
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:16,890
我不会公开提起任何名字
I didn't mention any names out loud.

271
00:13:17,610 --> 00:13:19,100
不会"公开"提起
No names "out loud"?

272
00:13:20,710 --> 00:13:22,020
那私下呢
What about whispering?

273
00:13:23,180 --> 00:13:25,130
别瞒着我  我会查出来的
Don't hold out on me. I'll know.

274
00:13:26,940 --> 00:13:30,320
作为幕后消息  我泄露了你的名字给几个线人
For deep background, I leaked your name to a couple of select sources.

275
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,620
以增加真实性  我没别的办法
I had to, for credibility!

276
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:32,760
你是调查韦恩案的警察
You're the Wayne murders cop.

277
00:13:32,770 --> 00:13:34,880
见鬼  他们就是这么找到她的
Damn it! That's how they got to her.

278
00:13:35,310 --> 00:13:37,470
花了这么久才找到她真是奇迹了
I'm surprised it took them this long to find her.

279
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,510
这都是你的错  丹特
This is on you, Dent!

280
00:13:39,850 --> 00:13:41,100
的确是我的错
I'll stipulate mea culpa.

281
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:42,570
暴揍我  随你便
Kick my ass, be my guest.

282
00:13:42,570 --> 00:13:44,170
但是咱们先找到洛夫克拉夫特
But let's find Lovecraft first

283
00:13:44,170 --> 00:13:46,080
让他叫停那些杀手
and get him to call off the killers.

284
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:49,250
他不在家  也不在他的办公室
He's not at home, he's not at his office.

285
00:13:49,250 --> 00:13:50,360
