that he keeps under his mistress's name.

289
00:13:57,260 --> 00:13:59,800
一个在史蒂文斯堡  另一个在上城区
One up in Stevensburgh and one, uh, uptown.

290
00:13:59,970 --> 00:14:01,260
上城区的那个我去
I'll take the one uptown.

291
00:14:03,590 --> 00:14:05,520
要是这俩孩子出了什么事
If anything's happened to these kids...

292
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:15,220
我们知道你和一个叫小猫的女孩
We know you ran with a girl

293
00:14:15,220 --> 00:14:16,410
是朋友
called Cat.

294
00:14:16,410 --> 00:14:18,010
她现在很危险
She's in serious danger.

295
00:14:18,010 --> 00:14:19,070
谁又不危险呢
Who isn't, right?

296
00:14:19,070 --> 00:14:21,310
世界就是这么疯狂
Crazy world.

297
00:14:21,990 --> 00:14:23,040
你要多少
How much?

298
00:14:28,350 --> 00:14:29,520
这是100
There's $100.

299
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:34,650
听着
All right, listen.

300
00:14:34,650 --> 00:14:36,470
我不知道小猫住哪里
I don't know where Cat lives, all right?

301
00:14:36,470 --> 00:14:38,860
她很注重这方面的隐私
She's... private about stuff like that.

302
00:14:38,860 --> 00:14:41,510
但我听说  她找了个新销赃人
But... I heard that she got a new fence,

303
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:43,130
因为之前那个被抓了
'cause her old one got popped.

304
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:44,360
他肯定知道哪里能找到她
He'd know where to find her.

305
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,530
这个销赃人是谁
Who's the fence?

306
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:46,410
我不知道
I don't know.

307
00:14:47,620 --> 00:14:48,910
但我知道谁可能知道
But I know who would know.

308
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:51,400
是吗  那又是哪位
Oh, yeah? Who's that?!

309
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,820
真是的  阿尔弗雷德  省省吧你
Damn it, Alfred, save your cheese!

310
00:14:55,830 --> 00:14:58,680
我用一摞硬币就能打到他招供
I can beat the truth out of this kid with a roll of quarters!

311
00:14:58,690 --> 00:15:01,030
去问菲什・穆尼
Yo, ask Fish Mooney.

312
00:15:01,030 --> 00:15:03,340
所有销赃人都归她管
She runs all the fences.

313
00:15:14,980 --> 00:15:16,650
抱歉吓到大家了
Forgive me for shocking you,

314
00:15:17,160 --> 00:15:19,630
但允许我给大家解释一下
but let me give you some context here.

315
00:15:20,740 --> 00:15:21,860
我很爱巴尼恩
I loved Bannion.

316
00:15:21,860 --> 00:15:23,170
起家时他就跟着我了
We came up together.

317
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:27,040
但他应该守好军械库的  可他失败了
But he was supposed to guard the armory, and he didn't.

318
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:30,690
而且也许  只是也许
And maybe, just maybe,

319
00:15:30,690 --> 00:15:32,090
是他背叛了我
he looked the other way.

320
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,990
我不确定
I don't know.

321
00:15:37,060 --> 00:15:38,520
那我该怎么办呢
So what do I do?

322
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:39,780
放任不管吗
Let it lie?

323
00:15:39,780 --> 00:15:41,010
老大  我们理解...
Boss, we understand...

324
00:15:41,010 --> 00:15:44,890
不管还有谁参与了  很快  就会祈求
Whoever else was involved will very soon wish

325
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:47,320
