they could die quickly, like Bannion.

326
00:15:49,130 --> 00:15:53,810
现在  我们所有人都得为家族利益着想
In the meantime, all of us must do what's right for the family.

327
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:57,310
你们每个人的税都要加25%
Each of your tariffs will increase 25%

328
00:15:57,670 --> 00:15:59,740
直到补上储备的空缺
until we've built the reserves again.

329
00:16:00,300 --> 00:16:02,610
无意冒犯  但这有点高吧
No disrespect, that's high.

330
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:05,840
是有点
A little bit.

331
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,890
你怎么想  菲什  我的要求合理吗
What do you think, Fish? Am I being fair?

332
00:16:10,230 --> 00:16:11,470
我们是一家人
We're family.

333
00:16:11,660 --> 00:16:14,500
有福同享  有难同当
We sink or swim together.

334
00:16:14,830 --> 00:16:16,440
你们都学着菲什点
You could all learn from Fish.

335
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:17,560
她就很信任我
She trusts me.

336
00:16:18,850 --> 00:16:20,660
你信任我  我就信任你
Trust me, and I'll trust you.

337
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:22,260
这是双向的
It goes both ways.

338
00:16:24,900 --> 00:16:26,160
吃饭吧
Let's eat.

339
00:16:41,650 --> 00:16:42,640
有电话
There's a phone!

340
00:16:42,650 --> 00:16:43,490
