Come on!

341
00:16:47,970 --> 00:16:49,140
我没有硬币
I don't... I don't carry coins.

342
00:16:49,140 --> 00:16:50,460
你有硬币吗
Do you have any coins?

343
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:52,110
没
Nope.

344
00:16:52,110 --> 00:16:53,400
一个子儿都没
Not a dime.

345
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:55,810
再说阿尔弗雷德对你有这么重要吗
Why does Alfred matter so much to you anyway?

346
00:16:55,820 --> 00:16:56,950
他不过是你的管家
He's just your butler.

347
00:16:56,950 --> 00:16:58,260
他是我的家人
He's my family.

348
00:17:08,840 --> 00:17:11,040
好运  小子  也许后会有期吧
Good luck, kid. See you around maybe.

349
00:17:11,040 --> 00:17:11,910
什么
What?

350
00:17:11,910 --> 00:17:13,430
-等等  -听着
- Wait! - Look...

351
00:17:13,820 --> 00:17:15,700
那些坏人是冲我来的
those bad guys were there for me.

352
00:17:15,860 --> 00:17:16,830
不是你
Not you.

353
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:19,730
你不必担心
You have nothing to worry about.

354
00:17:20,110 --> 00:17:20,890
回家吧
Go home.

355
00:17:20,890 --> 00:17:21,390
可是你说
But you said...

356
00:17:21,390 --> 00:17:23,530
我只是想吓唬你
I was just trying to freak you out.

357
00:17:24,510 --> 00:17:25,860
我逗你玩的
I was playing with you.

358
00:17:26,270 --> 00:17:28,090
你逗我玩
You were playing with me?

359
00:17:29,080 --> 00:17:30,310
这也太残忍了吧
That's kind of cruel, isn't it?

360
00:17:30,310 --> 00:17:31,200
是的
Yeah.

361
00:17:31,860 --> 00:17:33,050
听我说
No, look,

362
00:17:33,050 --> 00:17:34,140
你对我的看法没错
you're right about me.

363
00:17:34,140 --> 00:17:35,500
我并不友善
I'm not nice.

364
00:17:35,530 --> 00:17:36,630
不像你
Not like you.

365
00:17:37,560 --> 00:17:39,230
你待人非常友善
You got a nice way about you.

366
00:17:39,230 --> 00:17:40,590
-待人友善  -是的
- "A nice way"? - Yeah.

367
00:17:40,760 --> 00:17:42,640
所以我才说他们的目标是你
That's why I said that thing about you being the target,

368
00:17:42,650 --> 00:17:46,490
这样我们就可以在外多玩一会儿
so, you know, we could hang out a while longer.

369
00:17:50,100 --> 00:17:50,950
我懂了
I see.

370
00:17:52,320 --> 00:17:54,240
好复杂的心理
It's very convoluted reasoning.

371
00:17:55,120 --> 00:17:56,040
随你怎么说
Whatever.

372
00:17:56,370 --> 00:17:58,050
总之  很高兴认识你
Anyhow, it's been cool.

373
00:17:58,560 --> 00:18:00,050
-我要消失了 -你不能这么做
- I'm gonna disappear. - But you can't do that!

374
00:18:00,050 --> 00:18:01,830
-我不是在征求你的意见  -你不能消失
- I wasn't asking. - You can't disappear!

375
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:03,370
